text: Gerlacus Moes (10 August 1902 - 23 April 1965) was a Dutch swimmer. He competed in the men's 200 metre breaststroke event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1902 births Category:1965 deaths Category:Dutch male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of the Netherlands Category:Swimmers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:People from Bussum Category:Dutch male breaststroke swimmers
